          or conj x x' IN Conj x
   (2) x IN R+ /\ x' < om /\ y < om /\ conj x x' = conj x y ==> x' = y
       If x = #1,
       Then ox = 1                   by field_order_eq_1, x = #1
        and om = 1                   by ZN_order_mod_1
       Since x' < 1, y < 1, both are 0, hence true.
       If x <> #1,
